also observed in all three compounds. Our results\nshould motivate further investigation of the spin configuration on single\ncrystals of these iridium-based double perovskites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 17:53:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-01"}
