h mass distribution, hinting at the presence of dark matter\nsubstructure which has manifested as astrometric perturbations of the VLBI\nlensed images, posing no threat to the CDM paradigm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 13:59:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 17:13:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-06"}
