A-GSFC. We will discuss the\ninitial calibration tests, construction of the prototypes and the most\nup-to-date results from laboratory and beam tests with analog/digital\nelectronics and the SIPHRA DAQ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 15:10:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-18"}
